high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove the blue plate that is on the bottom shelf, then close the fridge doors.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the oven and look up.
Open the microwave and place the blue plate inside, microwave the plate for a couple seconds then remove it and close the microwave door.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the heated blue plate inside on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated blue plate inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, then left again to face the fridge.
Take the plate from the lower shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to go to the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave, above the stove.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Put the plate in the fridge, on the bottom left shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room and turn left to face the black fridge.
Open the fridge doors, pick up the blue plate from the left side of the bottom shelf, and close the doors.
Turn around, cross the room and hang a left towards the white stove.
Put the blue plate inside the microwave above the stove top, heat for three seconds, remove it from the microwave and close the door.
Turn around, cross the room and hang a right towards the black fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the plate on the left lower shelf and close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cold plate to chill in the fridge.
